WEBVTT

00:03.203 --> 00:04.601
Found my favorite.

00:04.704 --> 00:06.398
Black Jesus on skis.

00:06.468 --> 00:08.372
Why not? You go, brother.

00:08.474 --> 00:10.207
I'm partial to
the more traditional ornaments.

00:10.309 --> 00:11.809
Black Jesus reading the Bible.

00:11.910 --> 00:14.316
Baby Black Jesus on a walnut!

00:14.386 --> 00:17.004
Ho ho... No!

00:17.105 --> 00:18.725
We missed all the decorating.

00:18.827 --> 00:20.827
Don't worry.
We haven't put the star up yet.

00:20.943 --> 00:22.562
Which means we also
haven't heard Jermaine's joke

00:22.664 --> 00:24.197
where he says that he's the star.

00:24.299 --> 00:25.364
I can't do it now.

00:25.466 --> 00:27.400
So, who's gonna put me
on top of the tree?

00:27.502 --> 00:29.502
Where <i> is</i> the star? I just had it.

00:29.604 --> 00:30.903
Well, you know, it seems to me

00:31.005 --> 00:33.072
that whoever finds the star

00:33.174 --> 00:36.175
should be the one to hang it up
on the tree, right?

00:36.277 --> 00:37.376
Where's the star, T.K.?

00:37.478 --> 00:39.077
Why does Courtney get the honor
every year?

00:39.179 --> 00:40.278
Most families rotate

00:40.380 --> 00:42.614
so that none of the children
feel neglected.

00:42.716 --> 00:44.516
You're not my child.

00:44.618 --> 00:47.011
You're not <i> a</i> child.
Let's get this star on.

00:47.065 --> 00:48.086
- Okay, I'm gonna give you a boost.
- Here we go.

00:48.172 --> 00:49.502
- We ready?
- All right, Ma. Careful, now.

00:49.526 --> 00:51.256
Don't go too fast. Going too fast!

00:51.358 --> 00:52.790
Whoa! Whoa!

00:52.892 --> 00:55.059
Oh!

00:55.161 --> 00:57.661
Okay, that was not
a reflection of my boost.

00:57.763 --> 00:58.862
My boost was solid.

00:58.964 --> 01:00.364
All right. Can we wrap this up?

01:00.466 --> 01:03.601
I got a little Hanukkah thing
I got to get to.

